== Description ==

An easy way to create lightbox effect for WordPress editor's gallery block. Just turn on the plugin and use powerful lightbox.

Just create gallery by using "gallery" block and use lightbox gallery effect powered by fslightbox.js

Proudly created by [Kodefix](https://kodefix.pl/?utm_source=wordpress.org&utm_medium=description&utm_campaign=created_plugins "Kodefix")

== Frequently Asked Questions ==

= How plugin works? =

Plugin is filtering a content of posts and pages and append lightbox effect for all gallery blocks.

= Does plugin has any requirements? =

No. You can use this plugin with pure WordPress with Gutenberg editor enabled.

= Is the lightbox responsive? =

Yes. Lightbox is fully responsive - it scales to every device.

= Does the plugin use jQuery? =

No. Plugin is powered by fslightbox.js library.

